Just follow my lead.

14:50.973 --> 14:52.892
No, Reese.

14:50.973 --> 14:52.892
Whatever it is, no!

14:56.771 --> 14:59.315
Well, I guess you boys

14:56.771 --> 14:59.315
had some time

14:59.357 --> 15:01.108
