15:05.988 --> 15:07.031
And I understand how tempting

15:07.073 --> 15:08.825
a place like that can be.

15:08.867 --> 15:12.036
And I guess you kids

15:08.867 --> 15:12.036
really didn't do any major harm,

15:12.078 --> 15:14.163
so I've decided

15:12.078 --> 15:14.163
to let you off...

15:12.078 --> 15:14.163
Hi-ya!

15:14.205 --> 15:15.915
You idiot!

15:17.917 --> 15:20.044
Open it!

15:17.917 --> 15:20.044
It's locked!

15:20.086 --> 15:21.588
(groaning)

15:21.629 --> 15:24.924
Okay, I think

15:21.629 --> 15:24.924
I can cry now.

15:34.893 --> 15:37.854
(pneumatic drilling)

15:45.278 --> 15:46.654
My pleasure, Rusty!

15:46.696 --> 15:49.990
(voice echoing)

15:50.032 --> 15:51.992
