Well, this just plain

15:56.330 --> 15:59.375
hurts my feelings.

15:59.417 --> 16:02.002
Oh, man.

16:02.044 --> 16:04.004
Oh, ma... Stanley,

16:02.044 --> 16:04.004
I'm sorry, I did...

16:04.046 --> 16:06.173
Wait. I'm trying to see

16:04.046 --> 16:06.173
if I'm inspired

16:06.215 --> 16:09.009
by its symbolic bid

16:06.215 --> 16:09.009
for freedom.

16:09.051 --> 16:10.303
No. I'm just really pissed.

16:10.344 --> 16:11.930
Okay, don't overreact.

16:11.971 --> 16:13.222
It's just a snake, right?

16:13.264 --> 16:15.015
So, it's got to be

16:13.264 --> 16:15.015
around here somewhere.

16:15.057 --> 16:16.016
No big deal.

16:16.058 --> 16:17.059
(Patton barking)

16:17.101 --> 16:18.436
(whimpering)

16:18.478 --> 16:21.272
SPANGLER:

16:18.478 --> 16:21.272
Oh, my God, Patton! No!

16:21.314 --> 16:23.190
(two gunshots)

16:23.232 --> 16:26.026
Hi, Mom. Uh, I was just thinking

16:23.232 --> 16:26.026
about how much I missed you guys

16:26.068 --> 16:27.862
and I love you, and...

16:26.068 --> 16:27.862
I was thinking

16:27.904 --> 16:29.864
I should come for a visit,

16:27.904 --> 16:29.864
you know, like, today.

16:29.906 --> 16:31.491
There's a flight leaving

16:29.906 --> 16:31.491
in half an hour

16:31.532 --> 16:33.033
and I already booked it,

16:33.075 --> 16:35.035
so I just need

16:33.075 --> 16:35.035
your credit card number to...

16:35.077 --> 16:36.412
Well, honey, here's the thing.

16:36.454 --> 16:38.080
Right now, you are

16:36.454 --> 16:38.080
actually better off

16:38.122 --> 16:40.040
being as far away from me

16:38.122 --> 16:40.040
as possible.

16:40.082 --> 16:42.126
But...

16:40.082 --> 16:42.126
Aw, you got to trust me

16:42.168 --> 16:45.254
on this one, Francis--

16:42.168 --> 16:45.254
or, uh, should I say...

16:45.296 --> 16:48.299
"Olaf Mortenson"

16:45.296 --> 16:48.299
of Wheatville, Montana?

16:49.175 --> 16:51.886
(dial tone drones)

16:51.928 --> 16:54.764
You know, I have learned more

16:51.928 --> 16:54.764
in two hours with you

16:54.806 --> 16:57.767
than I have

16:54.806 --> 16:57.767
in six years of teaching.

16:57.809 --> 16:59.853
(sighs)

16:57.809 --> 16:59.853
So, did your life

16:59.894 --> 17:02.062
turn out anything at all

16:59.894 --> 17:02.062
like you planned?

17:02.104 --> 17:03.648
Oh, God, no.

17:03.690 --> 17:05.441
Oh, when I was a girl,

17:05.483 --> 17:08.862
I had all these crazy,

17:05.483 --> 17:08.862
romantic dreams.

17:08.903 --> 17:10.697
I wanted to be

17:08.903 --> 17:10.697
a blackjack dealer

17:10.738 --> 17:12.699
in an Indian reservation.

17:12.740 --> 17:14.659
Didn't work out.

17:14.701 --> 17:16.076
Stubby thumbs.

17:16.118 --> 17:18.078
Well, at least

17:16.118 --> 17:18.078
you have your home

17:18.120 --> 17:19.079
and your family.

17:19.121 --> 17:20.498
All I come home to every night

17:20.540 --> 17:22.959
are three howling cats

17:20.540 --> 17:22.959
and... Bob.

17:23.001 --> 17:24.084
Who's Bob?

17:24.126 --> 17:25.336
My showerhead.

17:25.378 --> 17:27.630
(both laugh)

17:33.052 --> 17:35.388
Do you have anything stronger?

17:35.429 --> 17:37.348
I'm way ahead of you.

17:37.390 --> 17:39.392
ANNOUNCER: ...and it looks like

17:37.390 --> 17:39.392
Rusty Malcolm

17:39.433 --> 17:40.894
will win his final race!

17:40.935 --> 17:42.770
Rusty!

17:42.812 --> 17:45.105
I can't believe

17:42.812 --> 17:45.105
they're missing this.

17:49.360 --> 17:51.612
(tires screeching)

17:57.201 --> 17:59.787
(crowd clamoring)

17:57.201 --> 17:59.787
What happened?

18:00.872 --> 18:03.165
Rusty do something?

18:03.207 --> 18:04.625
Missed it!

18:04.667 --> 18:06.627
What'd he do?

18:06.669 --> 18:10.130
(metallic squeaking)

18:10.172 --> 18:15.135
Men... a terrible tragedy

18:10.172 --> 18:15.135
has befallen us.

18:15.177 --> 18:19.223
At approximately 1700 hours,

18:19.265 --> 18:22.769
our beloved Patton

18:22.810 --> 18:26.355
was set upon by a serpent

18:22.810 --> 18:26.355
and devoured.

18:26.397 --> 18:28.357
I, myself, fired

18:26.397 --> 18:28.357
a few rounds

18:28.399 --> 18:29.984
as it slithered away,

18:30.026 --> 18:32.737
but hampered by a lack

18:30.026 --> 18:32.737
of depth perception,

18:32.779 --> 18:34.864
my efforts were useless.

18:34.906 --> 18:36.783
(sniffles)

18:36.824 --> 18:40.745
Now... after an incident

18:36.824 --> 18:40.745
such as this,

18:40.787 --> 18:43.163
certain questions arise.

18:43.205 --> 18:45.165
Leaving aside for the moment

18:45.207 --> 18:49.670
why God feels the need to take

18:45.207 --> 18:49.670
away everything that I love,

18:49.712 --> 18:52.006
that leaves us

18:49.712 --> 18:52.006
with the matter of

18:52.048 --> 18:55.134
who is responsible.

18:56.886 --> 19:00.180
Can you explain that,

18:56.886 --> 19:00.180
Francis?

19:00.222 --> 19:01.849
Yes, sir. I believe

19:00.222 --> 19:01.849
you lost that finger

19:01.891 --> 19:03.810
trying to restart

19:01.891 --> 19:03.810
the school lawnmower, sir.

19:03.851 --> 19:05.561
What is  in  the hand?

19:05.603 --> 19:07.563
They appear to be

19:05.603 --> 19:07.563
Raisinettes, sir.

19:07.605 --> 19:11.567
They are snake droppings,

19:07.605 --> 19:11.567
found in your footlocker.

19:11.609 --> 19:14.236
Now, what do you

19:11.609 --> 19:14.236
have to say for yourself?

19:14.278 --> 19:17.281
Sir, I'm obviously the victim

19:14.278 --> 19:17.281
of an elaborate conspiracy

19:17.323 --> 19:18.783
to frame me.

19:18.825 --> 19:20.284
It's just too perfect, sir.

19:21.243 --> 19:23.454
Two months!

19:23.496 --> 19:25.205
No hot water, no television,

19:25.247 --> 19:28.751
and an 8:00 p.m. curfew

19:25.247 --> 19:28.751
for the entire academy.

19:30.544 --> 19:33.213
Feel free to

19:30.544 --> 19:33.213
thank the cadet

19:33.255 --> 19:35.549
after I leave.

