19:40.262 --> 19:43.223
written across it?

19:43.265 --> 19:45.351
Yeah! Whoo!

19:43.265 --> 19:45.351
Yeah!

19:46.560 --> 19:47.687
Way to go, man!

19:47.728 --> 19:48.813
What?

19:48.855 --> 19:50.523
We hated that

19:48.855 --> 19:50.523
yappy, little rat.

19:50.564 --> 19:52.150
Let's hear it for

19:50.564 --> 19:52.150
Francis, you guys!

19:52.191 --> 19:53.651
(all cheering)

19:54.443 --> 19:56.195
(laughs)

19:58.781 --> 20:01.659
This is an improvement, right?

20:01.701 --> 20:04.662
Reese!

20:04.704 --> 20:07.331
Malcolm!

20:07.373 --> 20:08.833
(grunts)

20:08.875 --> 20:09.834
Hi, Dad.

20:09.876 --> 20:12.003
Hi. Where are your brothers?

20:16.298 --> 20:17.508
Oh, geez.

20:17.550 --> 20:19.426
Come on.

20:19.468 --> 20:22.180
Uh... what-what seems to be

20:19.468 --> 20:22.180
