Seeing people from all over,

20:36.986 --> 20:38.362
the different cultures...

20:36.986 --> 20:38.362
Hey!

20:38.404 --> 20:40.073
I don't want to be

20:38.404 --> 20:40.073
a hard case here,

20:40.114 --> 20:41.490
