Well, this all sounds

20:46.328 --> 20:48.664
pretty serious.

20:48.706 --> 20:51.125
But don't you worry,

20:48.706 --> 20:51.125
Officer Karl.

20:51.167 --> 20:53.794
They are gonna hear all about

20:51.167 --> 20:53.794
when I get them home. You see,

20:53.836 --> 20:55.922
I'm just sorry that they had

20:53.836 --> 20:55.922
to put you through all of this.

20:55.963 --> 20:57.381
That's not fair.

20:57.423 --> 21:00.176
And I, uh, see, I fully

20:57.423 --> 21:00.176
intend to pay for... Aah!

21:00.218 --> 21:01.594
(groans)

21:01.635 --> 21:04.013
Clyde, Kevin! Get to the car!

21:04.055 --> 21:05.223
(groaning)

21:05.264 --> 21:06.306
Go! Go! Go! Go! Go!

21:06.348 --> 21:09.018
Ooh!

21:09.060 --> 21:11.187
(chuckling)

21:11.229 --> 21:12.354
Okay.

21:12.396 --> 21:14.774
All right, men.

21:14.815 --> 21:18.694
Well, I hope you've all

21:14.815 --> 21:18.694
